 1916 Juli 4 Tuesday Up at 5.30 to work . move . Parad at 2 p . m . set out on our march of 8 mile . Sent on black bag blanket for transport . Carri equip overcoat . Thunderstorm break as we leav . Rain all the way . Do a forc march all the way . Thorough fag out at termin . Cross the frontier between Franc Belgium . Now on Belgian soil at Neuv Eglise . Crowd of 20 in tent wet cloth mud
